<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ms">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Master Plan: AI Agent OpenClaw 2026</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #0f172a;
            --card-bg: #1e293b;
            --primary: #38bdf8;
            --accent: #818cf8;
            --text: #f1f5f9;
            --muted: #94a3b8;
        }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; background-color: var(--bg); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.6; padding: 20px; margin: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 20px; }
        header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px; }
        h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .intro { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.1rem; }

        .phase { background: var(--card-bg); border-radius: 16px; padding: 30px; margin-bottom: 30px; border: 1px solid #334155; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
        .phase::before { content: ""; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 6px; height: 100%; background: var(--primary); }
        .phase-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .phase-num { background: var(--primary); color: var(--bg); padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.8rem; }
        
        h2 { margin: 0; color: var(--primary); font-size: 1.5rem; }
        .goal { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 20px; display: block; }
        
        ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
        li { margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; }
        li::before { content: "▹"; color: var(--primary); margin-right: 10px; font-weight: bold; }
        
        .output-box { background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1); border: 1px dashed var(--primary); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 40px; background: var(--card-bg); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
        th, td { padding: 15px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #334155; }
        th { background: #334155; color: var(--primary); }

        .check-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #334155; }
        input[type="checkbox"] { width: 18px; height: 18px; cursor: pointer; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <header>
        <h1>🚀 Pelan Strategik: AI Marketing Agent</h1>
        <p class="intro">Membina sistem OpenClaw yang fleksibel, selamat, dan autonomi (Visi 2026).</p>
    </header>

    <div class="phase">
        <div class="phase-header">
            <h2>Phase 1: The "Cloud Brain"</h2>
            <span class="phase-num">READY</span>
        </div>
        <span class="goal">Matlamat: Menjalankan OpenClaw di laptop sedia ada menggunakan API luar (Claude).</span>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Setup Software:</strong> Install OpenClaw di laptop/MacBook anda.</li>
            <li><strong>Integrasi Otak:</strong> Daftar akaun Anthropic (Claude API). Masukkan API Key ke dalam fail <code>.env</code> secara rahsia.</li>
            <li><strong>Tugasan Pertama:</strong> Gunakan Claude untuk draf konten marketing harian, susun jadual media sosial, dan balas emel.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="output-box">
            <strong>Output:</strong> Anda mula nampak hasil kerja AI dalam masa kurang 24 jam.
        </div>
        <label class="check-item"><input type="checkbox" checked> Selesai Fasa 1.0 (Setup Repo & Visual)</label>
    </div>

    <div class="phase" style="border-color: #818cf8;">
        <div class="phase-header">
            <h2 style="color: #818cf8;">Phase 2: The "Vault"</h2>
            <span class="phase-num" style="background: #818cf8;">NEXT</span>
        </div>
        <span class="goal" style="color: #a78bfa;">Matlamat: Memindahkan storan data dan memori ke NAS (Future-proof).</span>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Mapping NAS:</strong> Bina satu folder khas di NAS (contoh: <code>/AI_Agent_Data</code>).</li>
            <li><strong>Redirect Storage:</strong> Simpan semua History, Database, dan Knowledge Base (PDF/Excel marketing) ke folder NAS tersebut.</li>
            <li><strong>Data Ingestion:</strong> "Suap" dokumen jenama (brand voice, produk, harga) supaya OpenClaw boleh buat rujukan (RAG).</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="output-box" style="border-color: #818cf8; background: rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.1);">
            <strong>Output:</strong> Walaupun anda tutup laptop, semua "ilmu" AI anda tersimpan selamat di NAS.
        </div>
        <label class="check-item"><input type="checkbox"> Sediakan Folder NAS</label>
    </div>

    <div class="phase">
        <div class="phase-header">
            <h2>Phase 3: The "Internship"</h2>
            <span class="phase-num">LOCAL TEST</span>
        </div>
        <span class="goal">Matlamat: Mula menjalankan AI lokal (intern) tanpa bergantung 100% pada API berbayar.</span>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Install "Enjin" Lokal:</strong> Install Ollama atau LM Studio di laptop.</li>
            <li><strong>Download Model:</strong> Simpan fail model (cth: Llama 3.1 atau Mistral) di dalam NAS.</li>
            <li><strong>Hybrid Mode:</strong> Gunakan Local AI untuk rutin (sorting data), simpan Claude API hanya untuk tugas kreatif yang susah.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="output-box">
            <strong>Output:</strong> Kos API mula berkurang, dan AI anda mula berfungsi secara "lokal".
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="phase" style="border-color: #f43f5e;">
        <div class="phase-header">
            <h2 style="color: #f43f5e;">Phase 4: The "Final Boss"</h2>
            <span class="phase-num" style="background: #f43f5e;">ULTIMATE</span>
        </div>
        <span class="goal" style="color: #fb7185;">Matlamat: Hardware upgrade untuk autonomi penuh 24/7.</span>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Hardware Investment:</strong> Beli laptop/PC baru (32GB/64GB RAM) berdasarkan spesifikasi 2026.</li>
            <li><strong>Seamless Migration:</strong> Sambungkan laptop baru ke NAS. Semua "ingatan" muncul secara automatik.</li>
            <li><strong>Full Autopilot:</strong> Setkan OpenClaw berjalan 24/7 tanpa pengawasan untuk kempen marketing automatik.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="output-box" style="border-color: #f43f5e; background: rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.1);">
            <strong>Output:</strong> Anda mempunyai "Ejen Marketing Digital" yang bekerja sendiri di pejabat/rumah.
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>📊 Ringkasan Framework Timeline</h2>
    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Fasa</th>
                <th>Fokus Utama</th>
                <th>Otak (AI Model)</th>
                <th>Storan</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>Phase 1</td>
                <td>Kelancaran Kerja</td>
                <td>Claude API (Cloud)</td>
                <td>Laptop</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Phase 2</td>
                <td>Keselamatan Data</td>
                <td>Claude API (Cloud)</td>
                <td><strong>NAS</strong></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Phase 3</td>
                <td>Latihan Lokal</td>
                <td>Local AI + Claude</td>
                <td>NAS</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Phase 4</td>
                <td>Autonomi Penuh</td>
                <td>Local AI Power</td>
                <td>NAS</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

</div>

</body>
</html>